Usage

 The Configuration Template Plugin creates configuration to the output directory. The following examples describe the basic usage of the Plugin.

  To handle filtering this version of Maven Resources Plugin uses
  {{{http://maven.apache.org/shared/maven-filtering/index.html}Maven Filtering}} ${mavenFilteringVersion}.


* Generate configuration using template resources

+-----+
mvn config-template:make-config
+-----+

 Upon executing this command, a configuration package will be created in the build output directory <<<target\configuration>>>.
 This goal is bound to the <<<process-resources>>> phase.